-- Blauner Discusses New Book Dedicated to Boston (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-10-28T17:44:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-28/blauner-discusses-new-book-dedicated-to-boston-audio-.html
Andrew Blauner, the editor of the 
book "Our Boston: Writers Celebrate the City They Love," 
discusses how the book came together and how the proceeds will 
go to charity. Blauner talked with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and 
 Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 09:00
 